iv%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20talk%20to%20myself%20about%20our%20destiny%20in%20this%20war%2C%20I%20mean%20that%20we%20will%20not%20crawl%20forward%2C%20like%20the%20%5BUkrainians%5D%2C%20turning%20everything%20into%20%5Bdestroyed%5D%20Bakhmuts%20in%20our%20path.%20And%2C%20I%20do%20not%20foresee%20the%20easy%20occupation%20of%20cities%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhodakovsky%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20war%20is%20entering%20a%20phase%20%26quot%3Bof%20neither%20peace%20nor%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20come%20as%20Ukraine's%20military%20recaptured%20some%20key%20villages%20in%20the%20Donetsk%20and%20Zaporizhzhia%20regions%2C%20including%20Staromayorske%20and%20Urozhaine%2C%20the%20Institute%20for%20the%20Study%20of%20War%20(ISW)%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.understandingwar.org%2Fbackgrounder%2Frussian-offensive-campaign-assessment-august-14-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Vostok%20Battalion%20was%20among%20those%20who%20were%20pushed%20out%20of%20Urozhaine%2C%20with%20Khodakovsky%20saying%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20they%20left%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feuromaidanpress.com%2Fauthor%2Fmariatril%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22View%20all%20posts%20by%20Maria%20Tril%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3Ebecause%20their%20%26quot%3Bdefensive%20position%20had%20become%20untenable%2C%26quot%3B%20The%20Kyiv%20Post%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-component-name%3D%5C%22paragraph%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22cms.cnn.com%2F_components%2Fparagraph%2Finstances%2Fparagraph_5B811565-E1BF-06D6-8CC0-FE78591993D7%40published%5C%22%20data-analytics-observe%3D%5C%22off%5C%22%20data-editable%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3EBy%20taking%20both%20Staromayorske%20and%20Urozhaine%2C%20which%20are%20only%20separated%20by%20a%20small%20river%2C%20Ukraine's%20troops%20have%20gained%20a%20key%20position%20from%20which%20to%20attack%20Russian%20troops%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F08%2F16%2Feurope%2Furozhaine-donetsk-ukraine-reclaims-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%20reported.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20Deputy%20Defense%20Minister%20Hanna%20Maliar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fannamaliar%2F919%5C%22%3Esaid%20on%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20Ukraine%20also%20retook%20around%2040%20square%20kilometers%20of%20territory%20in%20the%20highly-contested%20Bakhmut%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhodakovsky%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmilitary-history.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FAlexander_Khodakovsky%23Malaysia_Airlines_Flight_17%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eis%20a%20former%20commander%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Alpha%20special%20unit%20of%20the%20Security%20Service%20of%20Ukraine%20(SBU).%20But%20after%20Russia%20attacked%20the%20Donbas%20region%20in%202014%2C%20he%20defected%20and%20became%20the%20security%20minister%20of%20the%20Donetsk%20People's%20Republic.%20He%20left%20that%20post%20in%202014%20and%20has%20been%20commanding%20troops%20in%20the%20Donbas%20region%20ever%20since.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%2C%20Khodakovsky%20suggested%20that%20the%20only%20way%20Russia%20could%20win%20the%20war%20is%20by%20using%20nuclear%20weapons%20against%20Ukraine%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Kyiv%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-0%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20previously%20said%20that%20his%20country%20will%20not%20agree%20to%20any%20proposal%20to%20freeze%20the%20current%20frontlines%20in%20its%20conflict%20with%20Russia%20in%20order%20to%20%26quot%3Bcalm%26quot%3B%20Moscow%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-will-not-agree-freeze-front-lines-calm-russia-zelenskiy-2022-08-23%2F%5C%22%3EReuters%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C