came%20the%20producer%20because%20I%20wanted%20to%20protect%20our%20film.%20Many%20times%20it%20happened%20that%20we%20were%20damaging%20the%20film%20in%20some%20way%20from%20the%20production%20sites%2C%20perhaps%20we%20were%20not%20giving%20the%20budget%20to%20it%2C%20not%20releasing%20it%20properly%2C%20not%20marketing%20or%20distributing%20properly.%20So%20I%20felt%20that%20if%20I%20produce%20myself%2C%20I%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20all%20that%20is%20right%20for%20the%20film.%20To%20mount%20such%20a%20big%20film%2C%20a%20big%20studio%20was%20needed%2C%20so%20we%20are%20making%20this%20film%20with%20Zee%20Studios%2C%20they%20have%20been%20good%20partners%20since%20the%20beginning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20we%20all%20have%20a%20belief%20that%20if%20the%20time%20is%20good%2C%20everything%20will%20work%2C%20maybe%20their%20time%20is%20very%20good%2C%20so%20we%20can%20also%20benefit%20from%20it.%20The%20trailer%20was%20attached%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20trailer%20and%20%3Cem%3EGadar%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20became%20such%20a%20big%20hit.%20We%20can't%20have%20a%20bigger%20marketing%20than%20that%2C%20because%20people%20might%20have%20seen%20our%20trailer%20even%20now.%20So%20we%20hope%20that%20we%20can%20also%20ride%20the%20wave%20of%20right%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20about%20the%20film%20Actor%20Aishwarya%20Lekshmi%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEven%20though%20it's%20a%20gangster%20drama%2C%20the%20emphasis%20was%20on%20the%20story%20and%20how%20well%20it%20was%20written.%20There%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20characters.%20Every%20character%20is%20well-written%20and%20is%20important%20and%20crucial%20to%20this%20film.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20all%20that%2C%20it%20was%20well%20mounted%20and%20for%20a%20gangster%20drama%20of%20the%20scale%20to%20actually%20come%20to%20fruition%20and%20be%20a%20brilliant%20film%2C%20it%20needed%20that%20budget%2C%20which%20I%20think%20Wayfara%20Films%20and%20Zee%20Studios%20pr