for-the-faint-hearted-shoaib-akhtar%2F%5C%22%3EBackstage%20With%20Boria%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Akhtar%20admitted%20that%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20huge%20pressure%20on%20the%20Indian%20team%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20as%20fans%20expect%20nothing%20less%20than%20the%20trophy%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20it%20is%20the%20pressure%20that%20you%20all%20put%20on%20the%20team.%20It%20is%20almost%20impossible%20to%20play%20with%20such%20pressure.%20Like%20I%20told%20you%2C%20it%20is%20as%20if%20you%20can't%20lose.%20If%20you%2C%20God%20forbid%2C%20lose%2C%20all%20hell%20will%20break%20loose%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhtar%20explained%20how%20important%20it%20is%20for%20a%20captain%20to%20soak%20pressure%20and%20help%20his%20team%20perform.%20The%20last%20captain%20to%20help%20India%20win%20an%20ICC%20title%20was%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22MS%20Dhoni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F700-ms-dhoni-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMS%20Dhoni%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20for%20Rohit%2C%20Akhtar%20feels%20the%20opening%20batter%20tends%20to%20panic%20and%20lets%20the%20pressure%20get%20the%20better%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%20and%20more%20important%20point%20is%20you%20had%20someone%20who%20could%20soak%20in%20all%20the%20pressure%2C%20and%20protect%20his%20teammates.%20He%20would%20not%20let%20his%20teammates%20feel%20the%20pressure%2C%20and%20that%20was%20the%20best%20thing%20about%20MS%20Dhoni.%20You%20won%20the%202007%20World%20T20%20under%20him%2C%20the%202011%20World%20Cup%20and%20then%20the%202013%20Champions%20Trophy.%20The%20moment%20Dhoni%20gave%20up%20captaincy%2C%20things%20went%20south%20for%20India.%20When%20I%20see%20Rohit%2C%20I%20keep%20asking%20this%20question%20of%20myself%20if%20he%20should%20have%20accepted%20captaincy%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%20I%20think%20Rohit%20feels%20the%20panic%20on%20occasions%20and%20lets%20pressure%20get%20to%20him.%20The%20press