0wonderfully%20acted%2C%20%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20created%20by%20Raj%20and%20DK%2C%20is%20a%20marvellously%20wacky%20crime%20drama%20that%20harks%20back%20to%20the%201990s%20and%20sees%20the%20darkly%20piquant%20side%20of%20men%20(and%20a%20couple%20of%20women)%20who%20derive%20perverse%20pleasure%20from%20murder%2C%20mayhem%20and%20meanness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deliriously%20spry%20Netflix%20series%20pans%20out%20in%20a%20twisted%20and%20toxic%20universe%20peopled%20by%20opium%20dealers%2C%20gun-toting%20gangsters%2C%20a%20vicious%20knife-wielding%20assassin%20with%20seven%20lives%2C%20an%20anti-narcotics%20officer%20with%20a%20troubling%20past%20that%20catches%20up%20with%20him%20and%20two%20diffident%20men%20with%20debilitating%20daddy%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gulaabs%20referred%20to%20in%20the%20title%20and%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20small%20town%20in%20which%20the%20story%20is%20set%20are%20outnumbered%20in%20this%20amoral%20world%20where%20adults%20and%20schoolboys%20alike%20thrive%20on%20crossing%20the%20line.%20A%20'line%20of%20control'%2C%20however%2C%20runs%20through%20a%20local%20dhaba%20and%20separates%20it%20into%20demarcated%20and%20inviolable%20spaces%20for%20two%20warring%20gangs.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20handful%20of%20innocents%20who%20reside%20in%20Gulaabgunj%2C%20nestled%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20dotted%20with%20opium%20fields%2C%20are%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20the%20two%20criminal%20cliques%2C%20one%20of%20which%20operates%20out%20of%20a%20place%20called%20Sherpur%2C%2030%20km%20away.%20They%20battle%20for%20control%20over%20the%20spoils%20of%20an%20illegal%20opium%20business%20that%20functions%20outside%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20cultivation%20of%20poppy%20under%20government%20licence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%20starts%20off%20with%20shots%20of%20a%20poppy%20farm%2C%20a%20sequence%20of%20two%20schoolboys%20discussing%20the%20girls%20they%20are%20in%20love%20with%2C%20and%20a%20chase%20scene%20that%20ends%20with%20a%20killing%20in%20broad%20daylight.%20So%2C%20all%20three%20key%20components%20of%20the%20plot%20-%20opium%2C%20love%20and%20violence%20-%20are%20packed%20into%20the%20opening%20moments%20of%20the%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20secondary%20elements%2C%20including%20a%20rivalry%20between%20two%20school%20students%20for%20the%20class%20topper's%20badge%2C%20emerge%20as%20the%20plot%20thickens%20and%20culminates%20in%20a%20dizzyingly%20rollicking%2C%20action-packed%20finale%20-%20an%20episode%20that%20is%20numbered%207%20and%208%2C%20runs%20nearly%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%20and%20has%20an%20intermission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEverybody%20in%20Gulaabgunj%20and%20Sherpur%20has%20an%20ulterior%20motive%20and%20a%20self-serving%20plan.%20These%20nefarious%20plans%20change%20frequently%20as%20the%20crooked%20men%20chase%20or%20flee%20from%20others%20of%20their%20kind.%20As%20small-town%20noir%20meets%2090s%20nostalgia%20in%20a%20landscape%20where%20the%20air%20is%20thick%20with%20intrigue%2C%20the%20soundtrack%20is%20laced%20with%20snatches%20Hindi%20film%20songs%20from%20three%20decades%20ago.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20murdered%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20Chapter%201%20is%20Babu%20Tiger%2C%20trusted%20aide%20of%20Gulaabgunj%20crime%20lord%20Ganchi%20(Satish%20Kaushik)%20and%20estranged%20father%20of%20motorcycle%20mechanic%20Tipu%20(Rajkummar%20Rao).%20Ganchi%20is%20furious%20at%20losing%20a%20key%20gang%20member%20and%20plots%20a%20reprisal.%20Tipu%2C%20in%20contrast%2C%20is%20almost%20relieved%20that%20his%20father%20is%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETipu%20is%20rid%20of%20his%20father.%20Jugnu%20(Adarsh%20Gourav)%20isn't.%20The%20latter%20is%20Ganchi's%20only%20son%20and%20reluctant%20successor%20to%20his%20father's%20empire.%20Narcotics%20bureau%20officer%20Arjun%20Varma%20(Dulquer%20Salmaan)%2C%20who%20was%20a%20deputy%20commissioner%20of%20police%20in%20Delhi%20when%20a%2060-crore%20scam%20(Bofors%3F)%20rocked%20the%20nation%2C%20is%20transferred%20to%20Gulaabgunj%20with%20a%20brief%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20hired%20killer%2C%20Atmaram%20(Gulshan%20Devaiah)%2C%20working%20for%20the%20Sherpur%20gang%20led%20by%20Nabeed%20(Nilesh%20Divekar)%2C%20Ganchi's%20former%20prot%26amp%3B%23233%3Bg%26amp%3B%23233%3B%2C%20is%20on%20the%20prowl%20armed%20with%20a%20slasher.%20Nobody%20in%20Ganchi's%20gang%20is%20safe%20as%20long%20as%20Atmaram%20-%20his%20name%20has%20Chaar%20Cut%20prefixed%20to%20it%20because%20of%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20he%20kills%20-%20is%20out%20and%20about.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArjun%20Verma%20does%20not%20arrive%20in%20this%20crime%20hotspot%20a%20day%20too%20soon.%20Ganchi%20has%20just%20swung%20a%20deal%20with%20Sukanto%20(Rajatava%20Dutta)%2C%20representing%20a%20Calcutta%20drug%20cartel.%20He%20has%20a%20month%20to%20acquire%20seven%20times%20the%20amount%20of%20opium%20that%20he%20usually%20produces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FpgEiBaF2mHA%3Fsi%3D3r9iO84mKlYmb0KE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20this%20deal%20and%20its%20shifting%20dynamics%20that%20are%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20farmers%2C%20the%20gangsters%20and%20the%20buyers%20go%20into%20overdrive%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20Gulaabgunj%20produces%20the%20requisite%20amount%20of%20refined%20opium%20for%20the%20Calcutta%20drug%20mafia.%20Arjun%20and%20his%20department%20swing%20into%20action%20to%20prevent%20the%20supply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlliances%20are%20forged%2C%20the%20police%20officer's%20relationship%20with%20his%20wife%20Madhu%20(Pooja%20A.%20Gor)%20drifts%20to%20the%20brink%20when%20a%20past%20liaison%20Yamini%20(Shreya%20Dhanwanthary)%20returns%20to%20haunt%20him%2C%20and%20matters%20of%20the%20heart%20come%20to%20the%20fore%20in%20uneasy%20circumstances.%20Tipu%20writes%20a%20love%20letter%20to%20school%20teacher%20Lekha%20(TJ%20Bhanu%20'Parvati%20Murty')%20and%20it%20boomerangs%20on%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENobody%20in%20Gulaabgunj%20appears%20to%20be%20high%20on%20opium%2C%20but%20whisky%2C%20which%20flows%20free%20in%20Ganchi's%20den%2C%20turns%20risky%20at%20one%20point%2C%20triggers%20a%20crisis%20and%20pulls%20a%20reluctant%20Jugnu%2C%20Chhota%20Ganchi%2C%20into%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20action.%20Talking%20of%20reluctance%2C%20Tipu%2C%20too%2C%20is%20an%20unwilling%20inheritor%20of%20his%20father's%20dodgy%20legacy%20although%20he%20has%20two%20unintended%20kills%20to%20his%20credit%20and%20with%20his%20spanner%20at%20that.%20The%20deed%20earns%20him%20the%20sobriquet%20of%20Paana%20Tipu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Tipu%20does%20not%20remember%20his%20father%20fondly%2C%20it%20is%20not%20only%20because%20the%20dreaded%20gangster%20left%20his%20mother%20for%20another%20woman.%20Baap%20ajeeb%20qism%20ka%20jantu%20hota%20hai%20(Fathers%20are%20strange%20creatures)%2C%20he%20says%20in%20one%20scene.%20For%20Jugnu%2C%20the%20struggle%20with%20his%20inheritance%20is%20not%20so%20much%20about%20hating%20his%20father%20and%20growing%20out%20of%20his%20shadow%20as%20about%20earning%20his%20old%20man's%20validation.%20I%20want%20to%20make%20dad%20proud%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWoven%20into%20the%20narrative%20and%20visual%20design%20of%20%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20sustained%20tribute%20to%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20and%20the%20Hindi%20cinema%20and%20music%20of%20the%20decade%20in%20particular.%20The%20plot%20and%20the%20soundtrack%20are%20littered%20with%20sounds%2C%20songs%20and%20references%20of%20the%20era.%20The%20series%20is%20a%20popular%20culture%20geek's%20delight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20names%20of%20the%20characters%20reflect%20an%20period%20that%20predates%20the%20birth%20of%20Rahul%20and%20Raj%20on%20the%20big%20screen%20-%20Gangaram%2C%20Lalkishan%2C%20Chandralekha%2C%20Mahendra%2C%20Atmaram...%20The%20titles%20of%20several%20of%20the%20chapters%20are%20drawn%20from%20songs%2Ffilms%20of%20the%201980s%20and%201990s%20-%20%3Cem%3EKasam%20Paida%20Karne%20Wale%20Ki%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EDo%20Dil%20Mil%20Rahe%20Hain%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3ERaat%20Baaki%3C%2Fem%3E....%20One%20chapter%20title%20takes%20off%20from%20a%20Bryan%20Adams%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20that%2C%20the%20series%20has%20a%20love%20ditty%20(composed%20by%20Aman%20Pant%2C%20who%20produces%20a%20delightfully%20retro%20background%20score)%20in%20the%20voice%20of%20Kumar%20Sanu.%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20the%20series%20designs%20the%20Satish%20Kaushik%20credit%20on%20a%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%2C%20not%20to%20forget%2C%20there's%20a%20mention%20of%20the%20cult%20kung-fu%20film%2C%20The%2036th%20Chamber%20of%20Shaolin%2C%20which%20Tipu%20watches%20with%20his%20best%20friend%20Suneel%20(Goutam%20Sharma%2C%20who%20also%20plays%20one%20of%20Suneel's%20two%20twins%2C%20with%20his%20real-life%20twin%20Gourav%20Sharma%20portraying%20the%20other).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaabs%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20studded%20with%20a%20quartet%20of%20wonderful%20performances%20from%20Rajkummar%20Rao%2C%20Dulquer%20Salmaan%2C%20Gulshan%20Devaiah%20and%20Adarsh%20Gourav.%20The%20larger%20cast%20of%20actors%20is%20no%20less%20impactful%2C%20with%20TJ%20Bhanu%20shining%20the%20brightest%20in%20a%20male-dominated%20series%20that%20touches%20upon%20the%20theme%20of%20gender%20and%20notions%20of%20masculinity%20in%20surprising%20ways.%20Pooja%20A.%20Gor%20and%20Shreya%20Dhanwanthary%20have%20much%20less%20to%20do%2C%20but%20they%2C%20too%2C%20make%20their%20presence%20felt.%20Vipin%20Sharma%20as%20Ganchi's%20righthand%20man%20Mahendra%20is%20solid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGuns%20%26amp%3B%20Gulaab