32.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fzeenat-aman-recalls-an-admirers-gesture-she-was-impressed-with-however-she-didnt-give-him-the-pleasure-of-her-company-on-a-date%2Farticleshow%2F102824227.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102824227.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EZeenat%20Aman%20recalls%20a%20cool%20gesture%20of%20an%20admirer%20during%20her%20earlier%20days%20in%20the%20industry%20when%20she%20was%20in%20the%20radiance%20of%20her%20youth.%20However%2C%20despite%20being%20impressed%2C%20she%20didn't%20go%20out%20on%20a%20date%20with%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fzeenat-aman-recalls-an-admirers-gesture-she-was-impressed-with-however-she-didnt-give-him-the-pleasure-of-her-company-on-a-date%2Farticleshow%2F102824227.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Rules%20For%20SIM%20Verification%3A%20Key%20Points%20To%20Know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20central%20government%20on%20Thursday%20announced%20new%20rules%20for%20SIM%20verification%2C%20discontinuing%20the%20provision%20of%20issuance%20of%20bulk%20connection%2C%20and%20making%20verification%20mandatory%20for%20dealers%20selling%20SIM%20cards.%20The%20new%20rules%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20government%20is%20working%20to%20tackle%20cyber%20fraud%20cases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAnnouncing%20the%20rules%20at%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20communications%2C%20electronics%20and%20IT%2C%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%2C%20said%20the%20government%20had%20deactivated%20over%2052%20lakh%20connections%20obtained%20using%20fraudulent%20methods.%20Over%2067%2C000%20dealers%20responsible%20for%20facilitating%20these%20illicit%20connections%20have%20been%20blacklisted%2C%20with%20300%20FIRs%20against%20those%20involved%20in%20cyber%20fraud.%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20occasion%20of%20World%20Telecom%20Day%20in%20May%2C%20three%20customer-focused%20reforms%20were%20released%20%5BCentral%20Equipment%20Identity%20Register%2C%20Know%20Your%20Mobile%20and%20ASTR%5D.%20Now%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20that%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20two%20more%20reforms.%20These%20are%20purely%20focused%20on%20user%20protection%20and%20reducing%20cyber%20fraud%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20key%20points%20from%20the%20new%20rules%20for%20SIM%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMandatory%20verification%20for%20vendors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20per%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20all%20SIM%20card%20vendors%20will%20have%20to%20complete%20police%20and%20biometric%20verification%2C%20with%20mandatory%20registration.%20The%20verification%20of%20SIM%20card%20dealers%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20telecom%20operator%20and%20violation%20of%20this%20provision%20could%20result%20in%20a%20penalty%20of%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E12%20months%20period%20for%20verification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20government%20has%20announced%20a%2012-month%20window%20for%20complying%20with%20the%20registration%20norm%20for%20existing%20sellers.%20The%20verification%20is%20intended%20to%20help%20in%20the%20identification%2C%20blocklisting%20and%20elimination%20of%20rogue%20sellers%20from%20the%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemographic%20data%20collection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUnder%20the%20KYC%20reforms%2C%20the%20demographic%20details%20of%20the%20customer%20will%20be%20captured%20by%20scanning%20the%20QR%20code%20of%20the%20printed%20Aadhaar%20in%20case%20of%20taking%20new%20SIMs%20or%20applying%20for%20a%20fresh%20SIM%20on%20an%20existing%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20Bulk%20Issue%20Of%20SIM%20Cards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Department%20of%20Telecommunications%20(DoT)%20had%20discontinued%20the%20provision%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fban-on-bulk-sim-card-connections-governments-move-to-check-cyber-fraud-4306305%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520verification%2520will%2520be%2520done%2Cnot%2520prescribed%2520in%2520the%2520rule.%5C%22%3Ebulk%20connections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20replacing%20it%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20business%20connections.%20Apart%20from%20the%20KYC%20verification%20of%20businesses%2C%20the%20KYC%20of%20the%20person%20taking%20the%20handover%20of%20SIM%20will%20also%20be%20performed.%20Individuals%20can%20still%20take%20up%20to%20nine%20SIMs%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20one%20identification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisconnection%20of%20SIM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20mobile%20number%20will%20be%20allocated%20to%20a%20new%20customer%2090%20days%20after%20the%20disconnection.%20In%20case%20of%20replacement%2C%20the%20subscriber%20will%20have%20to%20complete%20the%20KYC%20process%2C%20with%20a%20bar%20of%2024%20hours%20on%20outgoing%20and%20incoming%20SMS%20facilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20previous%20set%20of%20reforms%20announced%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20government%20launched%20the%20Sanchar%20Saathi%20portal%20for%20reporting%20stolen%20or%20lost%20mobile%20handsets%20and%20blocking%20them%2C%20and%20AI-based%20software%20ASTR%20for%20identifying%20illegal%20mobile%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692339900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndt