ch%20a%20meal%20they%20will%20prepare%20for%20you%2C%20that%20you%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20if%20the%20bones%20are%20those%20of%20beast%20or%20man%2C%20or%20of%20which%20beast%20and%20what%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20195px)%2085vw%2C%20195px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17154155%2Fimage-1224-195x300.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22195%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17154155%2Fimage-1224-195x300.png%20195w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17154155%2Fimage-1224.png%20352w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-668471%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ETall%20Tales%20By%20A%20Small%20Dog%20by%20Omair%20Ahmad%20(Speaking%20Tiger%2C%20August%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20things%20they%20have%20howled%20about%20me%20across%20continents!%20It%20is%20so%20shameful%2C%20about%20women%20and%20boys%2C%20about%20forbidden%20drink%20and%20sinful%20meats%2C%20about%20silks%20and%20gold%2C%20blood%20and%20shit%20(and%20they%20love%20their%20gore!).%20None%20of%20it%20was%20true%2C%20of%20course%2C%20but%20presented%20with%20just%20the%20right%20touch%20of%20plausibility%2C%20barked%20loudly%20enough%2C%20and%20repeated%20across%20town%20and%20city%20in%20a%20chorus%20of%20agreement.%20Even%20I%20started%20wondering%20about%20myself!%20Before%20the%20power%20of%20their%20tales%20what%20could%20I%20do%20but%20flee%2C%20hide%20until%20the%20dark%20of%20the%20new%20moon%2C%20until%20people%20forget%20and%20move%20on%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAh%2C%20but%20dogs%20don%E2%80%99t.%20Forget%20and%20move%20on%2C%20that%20is.%20They%20are%20famous%20for%20it%2C%20for%20staying%20on%20a%20trail%2C%20for%20scenting%20the%20faintest%20whiff%20of%20a%20scandal%E2%80%94here%20and%20now%2C%20or%20in%20the%20moment%20yet%20to%20come%E2%80%94and%20chasing%20it%2C%20and%20leading%20all%20the%20world%20to%20the%20poor%20sod%20who%20would%20be%20most%20embarrassed%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%E2%80%99ve%20all%20heard%20the%20story%20of%20how%20the%20dog%20accompanied%20Yudhishthira%20to%20the%20gates%20of%20swarga-lok%20itself%2C%20and%20that%20faced%20with%20Indra%E2%80%99s%20unwillingness%20to%20allow%20them%20both%20into%20heaven%2C%20Yudhishthira%20was%20willing%20to%20exchange%20places%20with%20his%20loyal%20companion.%20We%20are%20told%20that%20the%20dog%20was%20Dharma%20himself%2C%20more%20faithful%20than%20brothers%20and%20wife.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20story%2C%20one%20of%20thousands%20in%20the%20greatest%20of%20all%20stories%2C%20told%20long%20before%20the%20firangi%20thought%20up%20their%20paeans%20to%20loyal%20hounds%20and%20terriers.%20Why%2C%20even%20the%20beloved%20Prophet%20Himself%20is%20said%20to%20have%20blessed%20a%20man%20who%20went%20down%20a%20well%20and%20brought%20up%20a%20shoe%20full%20of%20water%20for%20a%20thirsty%20dog%2C%20the%20very%20creature%20whose%20saliva%20is%20haram%2C%20for%20it%20eats%20anything%20and%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20gave%20in%20to%20the%20rascals%2C%20the%20sons%20of%20bitches%20who%20claim%20the%20nights%20with%20their%20howling%20and%20yammering%2C%20the%20FM%20radios%20of%20all%20the%20nights%20of%20Hindustan.%20This%20book%20in%20your%20hands%20is%20proof%2C%20if%20any%20was%20needed%2C%20of%20my%20cowardice%20and%20capitulation%2C%20of%20their%20long%20manipulation.%20But%20I%20had%20some%20little%20shred%20of%20dignity%20left.%20I%20set%20some%20terms%2C%20lines%20in%20the%20sand.%20Gorakhpur%2C%20I%20said%2C%20the%20land%20of%20my%20father%2C%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20father%20and%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20father%20before%20that%E2%80%94centuries%20of%20bones%20and%20flesh%20turning%20to%20soil%20and%20mud%2C%20nurturing%20the%20soil%20that%20has%20nurtured%20us%2C%20aeons%20of%20a%20snake%20eating%20its%20own%20tail%E2%80%94Gorakhpur%2C%20I%20said%2C%20must%20be%20the%20muse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20the%20rascals%20would%20lie%2C%20spin%20fantastical%20tales%2C%20play%20with%20my%20mind%20and%20yours.%20And%20here%2C%20on%20my%20own%20soil%2C%20this%20soil%20mixed%20with%20the%20clay%20of%20my%20ancestors%2C%20I%20would%20stand%20some%20chance%20of%20fighting%20back%2C%20of%20taking%20the%20flights%20of%20fancy%20and%20tying%20them%20to%20earth%2C%20so%20that%20whatever%20tall%20tales%20I%20was%20fed%2C%20I%20could%20add%20a%20note%20or%20two%20of%20reality%20to%20them.%20I%20would%20defend%20the%20honour%20of%20my%20mitti%2C%20I%20thought%20to%20myself%2C%20the%20only%20honour%20they%20had%20not%20stripped%20from%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%20it%20was%20just%20one%20specimen%20of%20their%20biradari%20that%20they%20sent%20to%20me%3A%20Kallu%2C%20Kallu%20Maharaj%2C%20also%20known%20as%20kutta%2C%20kamina%2C%20harami%2C%20chor%2C%20and%20a%20string%20of%20more%20colourful%20names%20that%20my%20pen%20does%20not%20allow%20me%20to%20record.%20He%20seemed%20a%20nondescript%20character%20to%20have%20earned%20such%20fame%20from%20bakers%20and%20butchers%2C%20maids%20and%20washermen%2C%20a%20small%20dog%20of%20indeterminate%20colour%20and%20parentage%2C%20with%20a%20tendency%20to%20tuck%20in%20his%20tail%20and%20skitter%20away%20at%20the%20slightest%20sense%20of%20danger.%20But%20only%20to%20return%2C%20courting%20danger%20from%20a%20distance%2C%20until%20it%20was%20time%20to%20turn%20tail%20again.%20Wars%20have%20been%20won%20in%20such%20fashion%2C%20so%20for%20this%2C%20at%20least%2C%20I%20will%20not%20judge%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bit%20of%20a%20runt%2C%20then%2C%20this%20mongrel.%20Nothing%20remarkable%20about%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20when%20you%20looked%20closely%20that%20you%20realised%20he%20had%20the%20oddest%20eyes%E2%80%94they%E2%80%99d%20glint%20disconcertingly%2C%20sometimes%20blue%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20sun%2C%20sometimes%20red%20in%20the%20light%20of%20the%20moon.%20It%20was%20the%20spookiest%20thing%2C%20and%20I%20politely%20broached%20the%20subject%20at%20Professor%20Malik%E2%80%99s%20house%20at%20a%20quiet%20moment%20in%20one%20of%20his%20mehfils.%20He%20scoffed%20at%20the%20notion%20and%20told%20me%20to%20go%20easy%20on%20the%20liquor.%20I%20knew%20then%20that%20I%20had%20been%20forestalled%2C%20for%20it%20was%20only%20the%20dogs%20who%20told%20tales%20of%20my%20drinking.%20Somehow%2C%20they%20had%20planted%20their%20rumours%20even%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20greatest%20zoologist%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20did%20not%20enquire%20further%2C%20but%20I%20wondered%20about%20this%20dog%2C%20Kallu%2C%20whose%20tribe%2C%20we%20are%20told%2C%20cannot%20see%20colour%2C%20only%20black%20and%20white%2C%20with%20only%20their%20fantastic%20noses%20painting%20the%20world%20for%20them%20in%20vivid%20tones.%20How%20could%20I%20believe%20this%20about%20a%20dog%20whose%20eyes%20glinted%20in%20colour%2C%20and%20that%20too%20in%20different%20ones%20at%20night%20and%20in%20daylight%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20tales%20he%20had%20to%20tell%E2%80%94delivered%20with%20the%20skill%20and%20poetry%20of%20a%20dastango%2C%20or%20mumbled%20from%20the%20corner%20of%20his%20mouth%20as%20he%20ate%20a%20samosa%20stolen%20from%20my%20plate%2C%20enjoying%20himself%20as%20I%20goggled%20at%20what%20he%20said.%20I%20have%20been%20told%20that%20Zen%20masters%20debate%20whether%20a%20dog%20has%20a%20Buddha%20nature%2C%20but%20who%20would%20have%20thought%20that%20a%20dog%20would%20be%20so%20informed%20about%20the%20Buddha%E2%80%99s%20mother%3F%20And%20about%20tigers%20and%20shikaris%20and%20gangsters%20and%20banjaras%20and%20the%20wily%20firangis.%20About%20the%20Chinese%20who%20are%20now%20so%20Indian%20that%20they%20eat%20Gobi%20Manchurian%20and%20do%20not%20complain%3B%20about%20Gandhi%20and%20Kabir%2C%20and%20much%20else%20that%20I%20could%20never%20in%20any%20way%20confirm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20are%20all%20so%20mixed%20up%2C%20his%20stories%2C%20twisted%2C%20tangled%20and%20knotted%2C%20like%20the%20strings%20of%20the%20kites%20we%20used%20to%20bring%20down%20in%20our%20aerial%20battles%20back%20when%20we%20were%20boys.%20But%20I%20no%20longer%20have%20the%20wisdom%20of%20my%20youth%2C%20the%20felicity%20of%20mind%20and%20fingers%2C%20that%20I%20can%20untangle%20the%20knots%20and%20loops%20of%20any%20of%20Kallu%E2%80%99s%20tales%20and%20tell%20where%20it%20begins%20and%20where%20it%20ends.%20In%20my%20tongue%20they%20say%20you%20can%20never%20straighten%20a%20dog%E2%80%99s%20tail.%20How%20much%20more%20difficult%20to%20straighten%20a%20dog%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3Etales%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20then!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMay%20the%20clay%20of%20my%20ancestors%20forgive%20me%2C%20and%20not%20turn%20me%20from%20my%20mitti.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EExtracted%20with%20permission%20from%3C%2Fem%3E%20Tall%20Tales%20by%20a%20Small%20Dog%20%3Cem%3Eby%20Omair%20Ahmad.%20(Published%20by%20Speaking%20Tiger%20Books%2C%202023.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692325818000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17155442%2Fimage-1225.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-extract-a-dogs-tale-of-gossip-myth-and-mischief%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Every%20dog%20is%20a%20storyteller%2C%20but%20dogs%20do%20not%20write%E2%80%94you%20know%2C%20the%20whole%20thing%20about%20opposable%20thumbs%20and%20all.%20And%20once%20they%20find%20out%20you%20are%20a%20writer%2C%20they%20will%20want%20to%20tell%20you%20their%20stories%2C%20ask%20you%20to%20put%20them%20down%2C%20and%20they%20have%20so%20many.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fbook-extract-a-dogs-tale-of-gossip-myth-and-mischief%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%