s%20ramped%20up%20activities%20among%20the%20Meiteis%20to%20secure%20the%20%E2%80%9CHindu%20Vote%E2%80%9D.%20Segments%20of%20the%20Meitei%20community%20were%20untrusting%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20alliance%20with%20sections%20of%20the%20Naga%20community.%20As%20Hindu%20nationalists%20enlarged%20their%20grassroots%20presence%2C%20they%20identified%20flashpoints%20for%20the%20Hinduisation%20of%20the%20Meitei%20and%20promoted%20Vaishnavism%20as%20a%20method%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.internationalaffairs.org.au%2Faustralianoutlook%2Fsaffron-terror-and-hindutva-ideology%2F%5C%22%3Esaffronisation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2013%2C%202019%2C%20the%20RSS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-under-fire-for-misrepresenting-manipur-history-at-annual-event%5C%22%3Eappropriated%3C%2Fa%3E%20Patriot%E2%80%99s%20Day%2C%20inserting%20a%20depiction%20of%20%E2%80%9CBharat%20Mata%E2%80%9D%20(Mother%20India)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frss-under-fire-for-misrepresenting-manipur-history-at-annual-event%5C%22%3Ebetween%3C%2Fa%3E%20portraits%20of%20Manipur%20luminaries.%20Hindu%20nationalist%20schools%20started%20materialising%20across%20Manipur%2C%20operated%20by%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%2C%20Bal%20Sanskar%20Kendra%2C%20Bharatiya%20Jan%20Seva%20Sansthan%2C%20Bharat%20Kalyan%20Pratishthan%2C%20Ekal%20Vidyalaya%2C%20Friends%20of%20Tribal%20Society%20or%20Van%20Bandhu%20Parishad%2C%20Kisan%20Sangha%2C%20Rashtriya%20Shaikshik%20Mahasangh%2C%20Sewa%20Bharati%2C%20Sewashram%2C%20Vanavasi%20Kalyan%20Ashram%2C%20Vidya%20Bharati%2C%20and%20VHP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202019%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhats-been-done-to-tackle-external-aggression-by-aliens-sc-to-assam%2Farticleshow%2F68400824.cms%5C%22%3Espoke%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cexternal%20aggression%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fhow-setting-up-foreigners-tribunals-under-new-mha-order-can-be-a-dangerous-precedent-2181413.html%5C%22%3Epositioning%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20as%20a%20mechanism%20for%20expelling%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D.%20Akin%20to%20Nuremberg%20Race%20Laws%20instituted%20in%201935%20in%20Nazi%20Germany%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fescholarship.org%2Fuc%2Fitem%2F6w56781n%5C%22%3Eprejudicial%20citizenship%3C%2Fa%3E%20laws%20legalise%20Hindu%20ascendance%2C%20creating%20%E2%80%9Cracialised%E2%80%9D%20hierarchies%20of%20belonging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20an%20RSS%20leader%20stated%20in%20Manipur%20that%20the%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20principal%20obligation%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Forganiser.org%2F2022%2F10%2F07%2F96046%2Fbharat%2Fmanipur-protection-of-bharat-one-of-the-primary-duties-of-rss-swayamsevaks-says-v-bhagaiah%2F%5C%22%3Eprotection%20of%3C%2Fa%3E%20Bharat%2C%20preservation%20of%20its%20identity%2C%20and%20consolidation%20of%20%5Ba%5D%20Hindu%20world%E2%80%9D.%20An%20event%2C%20%E2%80%98Lok%2C%20Beyond%20Folk%3A%20Reimagining%20Bharat%E2%80%99s%20Future%E2%80%99%2C%20emphasised%20%E2%80%9Cnational%20self-hood%E2%80%9D.%20That%20year%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20re-elected%20to%20state%20power%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20required%20state%20approval%20for%20books%20on%20the%20culture%2C%20history%2C%20geography%2C%20and%20tradition%20of%20Manipur%20and%20pushed%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-to-implement-nrc-amid-exponential-rise-in-population-news-214585%5C%22%3Eimplementing%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20NRC.%20Presently%20applicable%20in%20Assam%2C%20NRC%E2%80%99s%20Islamophobic%20experiment%20to%20reconstitute%20Indian%20citizenship%20through%20legal%20discrimination%20impacts%20millions%20of%20Bangla-origin%20Muslims%2C%20who%20also%20self-identify%20as%20Miya%20Muslims.%20Next%20is%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20NRC%20in%20Manipur%20to%20evaluate%20documentation%20of%20descent%20for%20millions%20of%20individuals%2C%20crossing%20generations%2C%20to%20decree%20if%20non-Hindus%20of%20Manipur%20may%20be%20%3Cem%3Ebona%20fide%3C%2Fem%3E%20citizens%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsangh-parivar-golwalkar-rss-caa-npr-nrc%5C%22%3ECAA-NPR-NRC%20Represent%20the%20Culmination%20of%20Golwalkar%20and%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20Vision%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Hindu%20nationalist%20organisations%20are%20allied%20with%20Hindu%20Meitei%20groups%20across%20Manipur%2C%20reinforced%20by%20VHP%20and%20Bajrang%20Dal%20units%2C%20aided%20by%20reportedly%20107-120%20RSS%20branches%2C%2044%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Kalyan%20Ashram%20units%2C%20and%20463%20Ekal%20Vidyalaya%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisintegrating%20lifeworlds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20up%20to%20May%202023%2C%20majoritarian%20speech%20racialised%20the%20Kuki%20community%20as%20%E2%80%9COther%E2%80%9D%2F%E2%80%9COutsider%E2%80%9D.%20In%20January%20this%20year%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fpm-modi-transformed-congress-look-east-policy-into-act-east-policy-amit-shah-in-manipur%2F1301633%2F%5C%22%3Estated%20that%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9Cin%20just%20eight%20years%2C%20PM%20Modi%20has%20visited%20Manipur%2051%20times%E2%80%9D%2C%20claiming%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20had%20promised%20to%20make%20Manipur%20free%20from%20terrorism%2C%20today%20Manipur%20is%20completely%20free%20from%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%20In%20April%2C%20the%20Manipur%20high%20court%20ordered%20the%20demolition%20of%20three%20churches%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20construction.%20Since%20May%2C%20Hindu%20nationalists%20and%20majoritarian%20Meitei%20Hindus%20collaborated%20to%20cement%20ethnic%20supremacy%20in%20the%20region.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fs