ure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAiding%20our%20comprehension%20with%20hindsight%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fspecial-days-before-mha-was-to-finalise-kuki-accord-not-supported-by-cm-violence-broke-out-in-manipur%5C%22%3Euncovered%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20attacks%20began%20five%20days%20before%20Union%20home%20ministry%20was%20to%20sign%20a%20peace%20treaty%20with%20Kuki%20groups%20on%20May%208%2C%20granting%20an%20%E2%80%9Cautonomous%20territory%20council%E2%80%9D%20under%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%203%2C%20a%20mass%20burial%20laying%20to%20rest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-mass-burial-of-kuki-victims-postponed-after-mha-zoramthangas-intervention%5C%22%3Eapproximately%3C%2Fa%3E%2035%20Kuki%20Christian%20bodies%20was%20halted%20and%20postponed%20by%20the%20state%2C%20in%20a%20dispute%20over%20land%2C%20intensifying%20social%20trauma.%20Violence%2C%20rejection%2C%20and%20erasure%20disintegrate%20the%20lifeworld%20of%20the%20Kuki-Zo%2C%20already%20enmeshed%20in%20complex%20histories%2C%20%E2%80%9Clike%20a%20hammer%20to%20the%20heart%2C%20breaking%2C%20breaking%2C%20breaking%20it%20apart%E2%80%9D%2C%20mourns%20a%20community%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirectives%20to%20decimate%20the%20Kuki%20circulate.%20Unlike%20%E2%80%9Ccommunal%20violence%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20a%20term%20that%20masks%20radical%20dissimilarities%20in%20relations%20of%20power%2Fstate%20between%20Hindus%20and%20non-Hindu%20communities%20%E2%80%93%20the%20targeting%20by%20Hindu%20nationalists%20in%20Manipur-2023%2C%20Kuki%20leaders%20dread%2C%20is%20calculated%20to%20massacre%20their%20community%20through%20forcible%20assimilation%2C%20ethnic%20cleansing%2C%20presumptive%20statelessness%2C%20and%20calls%20to%20genocide.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20battle%20for%20the%20Hindu%20nation%20is%20sustained%20by%20psychic%20and%20physical%20brutality.%20Will%20further%20carnage%20before%20the%20next%20national%20elections%2C%20expected%20in%20May%202024%2C%20lead%20to%20the%20Hindu%20Right%E2%80%99s%20annexation%20of%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%9D%3F%20Resistance%20is%20profuse%20among%20marginalised%20communities%20in%20Manipur%2C%20as%20elsewhere%2C%20with%20solidarity%20from%20diverse%20allies.%20Yet%2C%20across%20India%2C%20dominant%20Hindus%20fail%20to%20collectively%20refuse%20ill-gotten%20privileges%20accrued%20through%20the%20deep-rooted%2C%20intersecting%2C%20and%20pernicious%20fault%20lines%20of%20caste%2C%20gender%2C%20and%20religion.%20This%20remains%20the%20pivotal%20impetus%20precipitating%20absolute%20nationalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAngana%20P.%20Chatterji%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchatterjiangana%5C%22%3E%40ChatterjiAngana%3C%2Fa%3E)%20is%20a%20co-chair%20of%20the%20Political%20Conflict%2C%20Gender%2C%20and%20People%E2%80%99s%20Rights%20Initiative%2C%20Centre%20for%20Race%20and%20Gender%2C%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EHer%20recent%20publications%20include%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fescholarship.org%2Fuc%2Fitem%2F6w56781n%5C%22%3EBREAKING%20WORLDS%3A%20Religion%2C%20Law%2C%20and%20Nationalism%20in%20Majoritarian%20India%3B%20The%20Story%20of%20Assam%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.oup.com%2Facademic%2Fproduct%2Fmajoritarian-state-9780190078171%3Fcc%3Dus%26lang%3Den%26%5C%22%3EMajoritarian%20State%3A%20How%20Hindu%20Nationalism%20is%20Changing%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1692275437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04223216%2Fimage-968.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fsiege-on-manipur-hindu-nationalists-war-for-ethnic-supremacy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Across%20India%2C%20experiments%20to%20forge%20the%20'Hindu%20national%20community'%20are%20predica