rt%20a%20business%20to%20utilise%20the%20land%20for%20dairy%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20start%20with%2C%20he%20completed%20a%20dairy%20science%20course%20from%20the%20National%20Dairy%20Research%20Institute%20(NDRI)%20in%202014%3B%20worked%20in%20companies%20like%20Mother%20Dairy%2C%20Amul%20and%20Nestle%3B%20and%20pursued%20a%20dairy%20automation%20course%20from%20Tel%20Aviv%20University%20in%20Israel%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20end%20of%202015%2C%20I%20returned%20home.%20With%20the%20technical%20help%20from%20a%20milk%20company%20from%20Israel%2C%20we%20established%20a%20dairy%20farm%20on%20our%20land.%20We%20started%20with%20milk%20subscriptions%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amanpreet%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20Gau%20Organics%20in%202016%20with%20his%20brothers%20Uttam%20Jyot%20and%20Gaganpreet.%20They%20bought%2027%20cows%20and%20started%20with%20milk%20subscriptions%2C%20later%20moving%20to%20value-added%20products%20like%20ghee%2C%20butter%2C%20organic%20jaggery%2C%20honey%2C%20sweets%2C%20etc.%20Today%2C%20they%20also%20sell%20cow%20dung%20cakes%20and%20manure%2C%20alongside%20training%20other%20farmers%20in%20doing%20so%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20notable%20about%20Amanpreet%E2%80%99s%20farm%20is%20that%20they%20are%20also%20able%20to%20cover%2070%25%20of%20their%20electricity%20needs%20on%20their%20own.%20We%20sat%20down%20with%20the%2032-year-old%20to%20understand%20how.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20the%20most%20out%20of%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBNshc_H6es%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCBNshc_H6es%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%